llip;&hellip;男人搵錢是天職，佢（丈夫）依家好似食軟飯咁！」<br />\n<br />\n「耕田窮極都有得食，鄰居都准你摘他田裏的菜；在香港連借鹽借油都唔得，鄰居一見我行過就閂門！」鄧生鄧太的願望很簡單: 兩年後鄧太拿到單程證，兒女接受免費教育，兩口子便可放棄綜援努力工作。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:05:20.000Z","msg":"番支那啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26aa0c1206d79e3ec1cdd4d97e17135d3e0bc764","tid":2211634,"uid":337986,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:07:43.000Z","msg":"仲唔死返去大陸？屌你老母傻系"},{"pid":"076a978147c75444e1d98ca74c7e5ca89bb645fa","tid":2211634,"uid":258377,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:08:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />條友中左肺炎未"},{"pid":"5a6f648973d9508f606470d10af031158b7fa798","tid":2211634,"uid":66527,"like":35,"dislike":2,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:11:04.000Z","msg":"咁你咪番鄉下 屌你老母臭系"},{"pid":"06edfb4ecaec3ad866fde9186c693e4b1d0f6e6c","tid":2211634,"uid":66527,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:11:53.000Z","msg":"又要屌又要留 屌你它母都唔知想點撚樣<br />\n呢d人唔死都無撚用 阻撚住世界轉<br />\n屌你老母"},{"pid":"921e1940ce412e40976fee248f66f781ad9fc008","tid":2211634,"uid":18999,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:12:03.000Z","msg":"唔洗po相已經記得咩樣"},{"pid":"5d5d06016a25fbbd0795fe910221bd2e0a7d60bb","tid":2211634,"uid":15511,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:19:46.000Z","msg":"個綜援婦抱孫未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c5be549045775774e23b08bbe9745570d31dd24","tid":2211634,"uid":77474,"like":16,"dislike":1,"